CompileFlags:
  CompilationDatabase: examples/basic/build/

  Remove:
    - -fno-shrink-wrap
    - -fstrict-volatile-bitfields
    - -fno-tree-switch-conversion
    - -fno-jump-tables
    - -march=*
    - -mtune=*
    - -specs=*

  Add:
    - --target=riscv32-esp-elf
    - -D__riscv
    - -D__riscv_xlen=32
    - -isystem/home/stzieske/.espressif/tools/riscv32-esp-elf/esp-15.2.0_20251204/riscv32-esp-elf/picolibc/include
    - -isystem/home/stzieske/.espressif/tools/riscv32-esp-elf/esp-15.2.0_20251204/riscv32-esp-elf/picolibc/riscv32-esp-elf/include/c++/15.2.0
    - -isystem/home/stzieske/.espressif/tools/riscv32-esp-elf/esp-15.2.0_20251204/riscv32-esp-elf/picolibc/riscv32-esp-elf/include/c++/15.2.0/riscv32-esp-elf
    - -isystem/home/stzieske/.espressif/tools/riscv32-esp-elf/esp-15.2.0_20251204/riscv32-esp-elf/picolibc/riscv32-esp-elf/include/c++/15.2.0/riscv32-esp-elf/rv32imafc_zicsr_zifencei_zaamo_zalrsc/ilp32f
